        },
        {
            "title": "A股半日跌   深股曾跌近1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股低開後續向下，滬股一度倒升，惟最終收跌，深股曾跌近1%，兩市成交合計13696.3億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指半日跌6點或0.18%，今早開報3839，跌24點或0.62%，中段最低見3837點，跌16點或0.41%，後段見3856點，升10點或0.26%，半日成交5958.67億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日報13339，跌106點或0.79%，今早開報13394點，跌51點或0.38%，早段見13453，升8點或0.06%，為半日高位，隨即向下，最低見13313，跌132點或0.98%，為半日低位，半日成交7737.63億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日跌19點或0.42%，報4574點，今早開報4576點，跌17點或0.37%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日跌37點或1.17%，報3198點，今早開報3222點，跌13點或0.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15295633-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%911",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240205_FI_source-ap_A-SHARE.png.webp",
